metadata.name: THE SATOSHI NFT COLLECTION #1
metadata.description: The Satoshi NFT Club is a collection of 10k unique, algorithmically generated young, adult & old versions of Satoshi Nakamoto, our core mission is to bridge the physical world and the virtual metaverse with our exclusive NFT collection. This will be an exclusive club for the Crypto community to chat with like-minded people, buy, sell and trade also. This one-of-a-kind club also provides you access to real-life events to build connections with crypto lovers and successful entrepreneurs. Commercial ownership rights are given to each unique Satoshi NFT you own.
